description:
This is the Clash of the Titans. Two of our strongest girls come at each other hard and fast today. Izamar Gutierrez defends her Championship Title today against Mistress Kara. Kara is the, Biggest, Strongest competitor on the Roster this year. Her strength puts her in a class of her own but her skill is what sets her over the top. Today she meets the Champ. Does she have what it takes to dethrone her?
Only one can reign supreme. Winner makes loser her bitch in round 4. Loser is DP'ed and treated like a sex slave.
title: Elite Wrestler is Destroyed on the Mats, Utterly Humiliated
